INSERT INTO `auction` VALUES (1,'CHANEL Pre-Owned\nCC stone-embellished brooch','Launching its first jewellery line in 1930, Chanel has since been known for creating elegant, timeless pieces. Crafted from polished gold-plated metal designed with the maison\'s signature interlocking CC logo, this brooch is adorned with emerald green glass stones.',3,'2023-12-23',775,12,'2022-11-18 10:48:37'),(2,'GOLDEN WHEEL HAIR WIG MAKING POST BED INDUSTRIAL SEWING MACHINE COMPLETE SET','GOLDEN WHEEL \nMADE IN TAIWAN\nHAIR WIG MAKING POST BED INDUSTRIAL SEWING MACHINE COMPLETE SET.\nEX-DISPLAY CONDITION ',8,'2023-12-14',1149,7,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(3,'Zamp Kart Helmet RZ 42 YOUTH Sizes CMR2016, Ideal for Go-Kart Racing & Oval Race','The Zamp RZ-42Y CMR Youth Racing Helmet is the ultimate Karting helmet with CMR2016. Designed for junior racers in karting that require the standard CMR homologation. Boasting up to date features the RZ-42Y is smaller and lighter but still filled with all the tops specs and features as the adult helmet.',8,'2023-12-14',299,8,'2022-11-12 00:00:00'),(5,'Refurbished Samsung Galaxy S21 Ultra 5G SM-G998B, 256GB, - Black,','The item shows no to minimal signs of use.• Performance: Fully functional. Minimum 80% battery life.• Guarantee: One-year guarantee provided by seller.Phones are shipped in a brown ECO wrap box and sent with a universal type c cable only',2,'2023-12-04',329.99,9,'2022-11-13 00:00:00'),(6,'L.O.L Surprise! OMG House of Surprises Wooden Doll House','OMG! Check out this fierce new house! The brand new, beautiful LOL Surprise OMG House of Surprises comes with 85 Surprises and measures 4 feet tall by 4 feet wide with 4 stories and 10 rooms, including a bedroom, bathroom, fully equipped kitchen, living room, pool, rooftop patio, movie theatre, diner and more. And each of the 10 fully furnished rooms fit all OMG fashion dolls and LOL Surprise dolls, including the 6 spinning transforming rooms that reveal extra features!\n\nMake your LOL Surprise dolls, and OMG fashion dolls experience glam life on a new level! Enjoy the interactive lights of the firepit on the rooftop patio, and check out the working elevator, the dishwasher in the kitchen, and more. With a spiral slide and a working elevator that fits 2-3 dolls, your LOL Surprise dolls, and OMG fashion dolls can now access each floor of this 4-story dollhouse! Plus, the furniture transforms, and the rooms spin!\n\nPour water into the pool and enjoy the summer heat with your cutest LOL collectables (not included). This dream house also includes a drive-thru and drive-in. Lights for the firepit are battery operated (included and replaceable).',6,'2023-07-02',113,4,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(7,'2023 Dunk Low SE \'Sashiko - Light Orewood Brown\'','The Nike Dunk Low SE ‘Sashiko Light Orewood Brown’ gives the heritage hoops shoe an artisanal makeover. The upper replaces traditional leather construction with textile twill in a subtle off-white finish with contrast brown stitching throughout. A crimson Nike tag adorns the tongue, matching the embroidered eyelets and Sashiko-style stitching on the toe box and heel tab. A color-matched rubber midsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.',3,'2023-09-05',117.67,5,'2022-11-16 00:00:00'),(8,'SEA MOSS (Irish moss) 100% ORGANIC WILD CRAFTED IN ST LUCIA','Our organic Sea Moss has been Ethically gathered and wild harvested from the clean and pristine Caribbean Sea of ST . Lucia by a small family of fishermen who harvested them from rock along the shoreline.It is a rich source of many vital nutrients and minerals.',5,'2023-09-03',15.99,4,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(9,'Large Beige Indoor Outdoor Mat Rug Garden Patio Waterproof Carpet Modern Rug','Brand new, Allergy Friendly, Antistatic, Dirt/Moisture-Absorbing, Dryable, Easy to Clean, Hypoallergenic, Kid Friendly, Noise-Reducing, Pet Friendly, Stain Resistant, Suitable for Floor Heating, Washable',1,'2023-08-13',48.99,12,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(10,'PAIR OF LARGE VINTAGE MURANO STYLE CRYSTAL WALL LIGHTS SCONCES','Beautiful Large Pair Vintage Murano Style Wall Lights Crystal Sconces \nWith Glass Candles\nGlass cup holders with 6 pears drop crystals on each one\nWith plastic covered arms covered in flower crystals\nWith large pear crystals along the arms and centre \nOn a brass back plate\nIn good condition for age\nApprox size: 32cm Length X 22cm Wide X 43cm Height \nHeavy and impressive',9,'2023-10-21',150,12,'2022-11-13 00:00:00'),(11,'Complete set of 50 1964 Daystar-Villa Outer limits bubble gum cards','condition: Very good, Complete set of 50 Outer Limits Daystar-Villa bubble gum cards. Printed in England. Each card just over 3\" by 2\". From 1964',9,'2023-11-20',95,12,'2022-11-13 00:00:00'),(12,'LEDBURY 3F - ANGLED CORNER DAYBED WITH COFFEE TABLE','Our Ledbury 3F is a multifunctional modular set that simply oozes style and opulence. Seating up to 7 people, this chic & ultra-modern set can be used as both a daybed and a sofa, making the multi-purpose design ideal for a variety of occasions. So whether you\'re inviting friends over for an outdoor social gathering or simply relaxing alone in the sun, do it in style with this incredibly luxurious daybed & sofa set One Sofa\r Two Single Armchairs\r One Coffee Table\r Very good condition, barely used',1,'2022-11-08',725,9,'2022-11-17 19:36:03'),(13,'Salter Coffee Machine Espresso Maker Caffé Barista Pro 15-Bar Pump Frothing Wand','Salter EK4369 Caffé Barista Pro Espresso Machine, Cappuccino, Latte and Coffee Maker, 15-Bar Pressure Pump, Milk Frothing Wand, Removable Drip Tray, 2 Cups at Once, Durable Stainless Steel Filte',1,'2023-12-10',74.99,12,'2022-11-18 10:51:46'),(17,'Ribble R872 - Sport\nShimano TiagraWheel 18 Spd Black Green','\nDesigned in-house and expertly handcrafted from carbon, the fast, light and highly agile R872 offers the perfect blend of performance and comfort. Its lightweight ride quality makes it soar on the climbs and fly on the flat. Whether you plan to race your friends for the café stop or attempt your longest-ever solo ride, the smooth road performance and long-haul comfort of the R872 deliver a class-leading ride quality. The R872 is the perfect getaway vehicle for fast, fun weekends of open-road exploration.',7,'2023-08-17',999.99,1,'2022-11-14 00:00:00'),(19,'Rare 2p Two Pence 1971','rare 2 pence from 1971 with mona lisa',9,'2023-12-31',500,7,'2022-11-13 00:00:00'),(21,'Shark FlexStyle 5-in-1 Air Styler & Hair Dryer | Certified Refurbished','Powerful, fast drying meets versatile multi-styling. With a single twist, Shark FlexStyle rotates between a powerful hair dryer and a 5-in-1 styling wand. Transform your routine. Flex your style.',2,'2023-07-23',219.99,9,'2022-11-14 00:00:00'),(22,'MacBook Pro A2141 16” TouchBar Faulty For Spares Or Parts','Broken display as shown in image 1 - backlight on and occasionally shows a distorted image, for parts and spares.',2,'2023-10-25',39.99,8,'2022-11-15 00:00:00'),(24,'240v SINGLE PHASE ELECTRIC MOTOR 0.18kW-4.0kW 1400RPM & 2800RPM B3 B5 B14 2&4P',' A brand-new, unused, unopened and undamaged item in original retail packaging (where packaging is applicable). If the item comes direct from a manufacturer, it may be delivered in non-retail packaging, such as a plain or unprinted box or plastic bag. This range of aluminium single phase capacitor start capacitor run motors is suitable for many different industrial applications. The start capacitor design is suitable for medium starting torque applications such as pumps or compressors.\nStarting torque 1.8 - 2.5 times the rated torque. ',7,'2023-10-17',84.66,8,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(25,'Empty Clear Gelatine/Hpmc Vegetarain/Pullulan Vegan Capsules Sizes000#00#0#1#2#4',' GELATIN  Empty Clear Capsules\n The raw material for our capsules is sourced from Rousselot, the largest supplier of high-quality bovine bone gelatin.\n  With four locking points in a unique pre-locking ring to prevent separation of the capsule during transportation.\n High-reliability closure on all types of filling machines. Reduced incidence of split capsules and dented ends. To be filled by filling machines.',5,'2023-11-01',795.99,1,'2022-11-11 00:00:00'),(26,'Steiff bears\nSteiff King Charles III Coronation Long To Reign Over Us Bear','We are very happy to present a very special teddy bear named ‘KING CHARLES III’ who will be crowned on Saturday 6th May 2023.\n\nKING CHARLES is made of grey violet mohair and is fully jointed (which means you can move his head, arms and legs).\nKING CHARLES has felt paw pads, magnificent royal face and shiny black eyes, hand stitched black nose and mouth - together with traditional ears.\n\nKING CHARLES is wearing a robe which is finished with a white edging and kept together with little buttons.\n\nAt the back of this special bear is a turnable button - just wind up the button and you will hear \'God Save the King\'.\n\nLittle editon of just 2,022 pieces.\n\nThis bear is scheduled to arrive during July, August, September 2023 for orders placed before 13.00 6th May, orders placed after this delivery expected November/December\n\nSurface washable.\n\nWhite label with famous Steiff gold plated button in the ear.',9,'2023-12-10',295,2,'2022-11-16 00:00:00'),(27,'Tory Burch GOOD LUCK TRAINER','The shape of a wishbone — a symbol of luck — embedded in its sole. Designed for forward momentum...because luck is what you make of it. Symbols of luck from around the world have always fascinated Tory. The evil eye, knocking on wood and, a family tradition, carrying a red ribbon whenever she travels. \n\nOur trainer combines flattering lines and comfort: a deep ankle scoop that elongates the leg; an oversized ergonomic sole for lift; and our Double T logo set at an angle. Innovative construction balances support and softness. A structural wishbone within the cushioned midsole acts as a cambrion, reinforcing the shoe\'s internal support system. Size 7 available.',3,'2023-09-10',290,9,'2022-11-17 17:00:21'),(29,'Henry Bagged Corded Cylinder Vacuum Cleaner - Red','With over 15 million Henry\'s made, and most still in use today, he really is the vacuum you can trust. Packed full of great features to make cleaning easy, including a huge capacity, versatile toolkit and super long-reach, trouble-free rewind cable. Carpets, hard-floors, cars, stairs, DIY nothing beats a Henry for versatility.\n\nA Tool for Every Job - Henry\'s versatile toolkit includes: Combi Floor Tool, Dusting Tool, Crevice Tool and Brush & Mattress Tool.\n\nHuge Capacity - Less emptying with a capacity up to x5 bigger than many bagless vacuums.\n\nStores Neatly Away - On-board tool storage means tools are always to hand and neatly packed away.\n\nWhat Goes in, Stays in - Henry Bags lock in all the dust, meaning emptying with no dust and no mess.',1,'2023-12-31',130,4,'2022-11-17 00:00:00'),(30,'HP ENVY 34-c1002na WUHD All-in-One PC - NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 3050 – Core™ i7','From a rejuvenated Start menu, to new ways to connect to your favorite people, news, games, and content—Windows 11 is the place to think, express, and create in a natural way.[d]',2,'2023-06-24',2307.58,5,'2022-11-17 00:00:00'),(31,'KITCHEN AID ARTISAN FOOD MIXER MIDNIGHT BLUE 1 BALLOON WHISK GREAT CONDITION','KITCHEN AID ARTISAN FOOD MIXER MIDNIGHT BLUE 1 BALLOON WHISK GREAT CONDITION.',1,'2023-07-25',250,5,'2022-11-16 00:00:00'),(32,'2012 audi a4 spares or repair','audi a4 spares or repairs, Engine seized due to oil pump failure Few marks here and there and some front bumper damage Gearbox and everything else fine, Mot until 20/12/23\n164240 miles\nDoes not start Buyer will need recovery.',7,'2023-07-17',510,5,'2022-11-15 00:00:00'),(33,'POKÉMON TCG: SWORD AND SHIELD ULTRA-PREMIUM COLLECTION – CHARIZARD','Celebrate the Sword & Shield Series and the era of Pokémon V, Pokémon VMAX, and Pokémon VSTAR with a hotshot who knows how to put all that power to good use! Charizard turns up the heat as a trio of promo cards with an etched foil treatment, and its Gigantamax form shows off blazing style on a playmat, metal coin, and set of card sleeves. Metal dice and condition markers round out this ultimate set of gameplay accessories. And as you open the huge stack of booster packs inside this box, take a journey through the Sword & Shield Series with an original booklet full of images and stats!\n\n',6,'2023-08-23',79.99,4,'2022-11-13 00:00:00'),(34,'Refurbished - Pink Chrome Hoverboard + Bluetooth and LED wheels UL2272 Certified','Refurbished ZIMX HB4 Hoverboard/Swegway',8,'2023-09-03',119.99,1,'2022-11-15 00:00:00'),(35,'Genuine Sony WF-1000XM4 True Wireless Noise Cancelling Earbud Right Ear Only (R)','Used: An item that has been previously used. The item may have some signs of cosmetic wear, but is fully operational and functions as intended. fully working, Genuine Sony WF-1000XM4 True Wireless Noise Cancelling Earbud Right Ear Only (R).',2,'2023-11-01',49.99,9,'2022-11-17 19:35:32'),(40,'Hermes - O\'Kelly pendant, small model','Pendant in Swift calfskin with rose gold plated hardware.\nThe O\'Kelly line gives pride of place to the eponymous bag\'s padlock. Here, it is slimmed down and attached to a stylized leather padlock that follows it like a shadow.\n\nMade in France\n\nTotal chain length: 45 cm | Pendant size: 3 cm x 1.5 cm',3,'2023-08-31',295.99,9,'2022-11-17 17:11:17'),(61,'bodytrain exercise bike','indoor exercise bike with 10 settings at working condition',4,'2023-08-31',199.99,12,'2022-11-18 10:51:46');
