INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (3,'Whey Protein Strawberry','Premium whey packed with 21g of protein per serving, for the everyday protein you need from a quality source.\r\n\r\nAnd where does this whey come from? The same cows that produce your milk and cheese — simply filtered, evaporated, and spray-dried to produce all-natural nutritionals.\r\n\r\nRanked Grade A by independent tester Labdoor for both quality and value, Impact Whey Protein is officially certified as one of the best protein powders on the market.','(Per serving 25g)Cals: 103 Fat: 1.9g Saturated fat: 1.3g Sugar: 1.0g,Protien 21g,Salt 0.13g',2,21,15052023,'15052023','proteinpowder.png'),(4,'Whey Protein 360 Extreme Blueberry Cheesecake','Whey Protein 360 Extreme is a premium protein blend designed for those wanting more out of their shakes: more protein, more nutrition, more delicious flavours.\r\n\r\nIts unique formulation boasts 26g of protein infused with an innovative blend of essential vitamins and minerals, as well as added glutamine and digestive enzymes to ensure that you get a shake that not only tastes amazing but delivers on nutrition.\r\n\r\nWhey Protein 360 Extreme is high in protein and low in fat, making it the perfect shake to enjoy before or after a workout, especially when your goal is to build muscle.','Nutritional Info\r\nValues based on:	per 100g	per 35g serving	\r\nEnergy (kJ)	1560	546	\r\nEnergy (kcal)	382	134	\r\nFat (g)	2.6	0.9	\r\nof which Saturates (g)	1.8	0.6	\r\nCarbohydrates (g)	13	4.4	\r\nof which Sugars (g)	8.4	2.9	\r\nFibre (g)	0.6	0.2	\r\nProtein (g)	76	26	\r\nSalt (g)	1.26	0.44	',2,24,1000,'15052023','64629b03346b5.png'),(6,'Multivitamin Gummies','Welcome to the simplest and tastiest way to get your daily dose of essential vitamins and minerals.\r\n\r\nExploding with Mixed Fruits flavours, our Chewable Vegan Friendly - Multivitamin Gummies are packed with essential vitamins to help support your immune system, fight fatigue and keep your body in peak condition.\r\n\r\n+ Packed with essential vitamins and minerals\r\n+ Tastes just like a gummy sweet.\r\n+ Chewable and easy to swallow\r\n+ Suitable for Vegans and Vegetarians','Nutritional Info\r\nValues based on:	per 2 gummies	*RI%\r\nVitamin A	400ug	50%\r\nVitamin D	5ug	100%\r\nVitamin E	12mg	100%\r\nVitamin C	80mg	100%\r\nVitamin B3	16mg	100%\r\nBiotin	50ug	100%	',1,23,50,'15052023','64629d73d5263.png'),(7,'Ridiculous Vegan Protein Bar','Ridiculous Vegan Protein Bar has been thoughtfully designed to balance your conscience and your cravings. It\'s fully plant based and purposefully palm oil free. It\'s also low in sugar, high in protein & high in fibre, keeping you fuller for longer in less than 200 cals a bar*.\r\n\r\nFree from gluten, preservatives and containing zero artificial flavours and colours it also uses only natural sweeteners. Yet it’s still been crafted to deliver a \'ridiculous\' multi-layered experience of a biscuit dough, nuts and caramel body, smothered in plant based chocolate & smattered with high protein crispies. It’s quite simply a vegan bar like no other.\r\nBoxes of Ridiculous Vegan Bars stacked with a blue background\r\nWhy Buy Ridiculous Vegan Protein Bars\r\nFully Plant Based\r\n\r\nLess Than 200 Calories Per bar\r\n\r\nHigh Protein, Low Sugar\r\n\r\nMultiple Levels of Indulgence\r\n\r\nHigh In Fibre','Ingredients\r\n\r\nProtein Blend (Pea Protein Isolate, Soy Protein Isolate), Sweetener: Maltitol, Flavoured Cocoa Butter with Rice and Sweetener (15%): (Cocoa Butter, Rice Powder (Rice Syrup, Rice Starch, Rice Flour), Raw Sugar, Natural Flavouring), Soy Protein Nuggets (Soy Protein Isolate, Tapioca Starch, Sea Salt), Chicory Root Fibre, Humectant: Vegetable Glycerine, Almond Paste, Coconut Oil, Emulsifier: Sunflower Lecithin, Cocoa Butter, Natural Flavouring, Thickener: Gum Acacia, Himalayan Salt, Green Tea Extract, Sweetener (Steviol Glycosides).',3,15,1000,'15052023','6464fb7fc3a82.png'),(8,'Protein Double Chocolate Cookies','hey are a healthier version of a typical chocolate-covered biscuit, and also a great alternative to a traditional protein bar.\r\n\r\nThey are of course high in protein and as with every Protein Works snack, taste amazing. Choose from two indulgent flavours: Salted Caramel Crunch and Double Chocolate Crisp.\r\n\r\nThey also come with a real crunch, making them a tempting and nutritious snack to enjoy any time of day.\r\n\r\nEach box contains 18 high protein biscuits, packed into 9 double foil-fresh packs, making them ideal to snack large or snack small, wherever you need a protein boost. ','Nutritional Info\r\nValues based on:	per 100g	per 50g serving (2 Biscuits)\r\nEnergy (kJ)	1850	925\r\nEnergy (kcal)	440	220\r\nFat (g)	24	12\r\nof which Saturates (g)	13	6.7\r\nCarbohydrates (g)	47	23\r\nof which Sugars (g)	8.6	4.3\r\nFibre (g)	0.7	0.4\r\nProtein (g)	22	11\r\nSalt (g)	1.3	0.65',3,9,300,'15052023','6464fc3175234.png'),(10,'Protein Mug Cake Mix Banana Cake','The time has come to welcome cake back in your diet. With our Protein Mug Cake Mix, you can whip up a nutritious, soft, and delicious protein cake in under two minutes.\r\n\r\nEach cake is a nutritional powerhouse, packing 148 calories, 5 grams of protein, under 1g of sugar, under 3g of fat, and a whooping 8.6g of fibre.\r\n\r\nThere is no better protein cake on the planet, let alone a protein cake you can make at home – or in the office - in a matter of minutes. Our Protein Mug Cake Mix is the perfect way to satisfy your sweet tooth.\r\n\r\nEach mug cake takes under two minutes to make in the microwave and the result? A warm and delicious cake for you to enjoy after a workout, as a snack, or whenever you most crave something indulgent yet secretly good for you.','Wheat Flour (Calcium Carbonate, Iron, Niacin, Thiamin), Fructo-Oligosaccharides, Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk) (Emulsifier: Sunflower Lecithin), Raising Agent (Disodium Diphosphate, Sodium hydrogen Carbonate, Monocalcium Phosphate), Medium Chain Tri-Glycerides [MCT, Sodium Caseinate (Milk), Glucose Syrup Solids, Emulsifier: E472c], Flavouring, Waxy Maize Starch, Colour (Curcumin), Sweetener (Sucralose).',3,14,111,'15052023','6464fd645d6b7.png'),(11,'Protein Peanut Butter','Only Peanuts from Protein Works is made simply from 100% natural roasted peanuts.\r\n\r\nUnlike standard brands ours contains absolutely no added sugar, palm oil or salt.\r\n\r\nThis nutrient dense peanut butter champions at least 25g of protein per 100g.','Nutritional Info\r\nValues based on:	per 100g\r\nEnergy (kJ)	2487\r\nEnergy (kcal)	606\r\nFat (g)	52\r\nof which Saturates (g)	6.4\r\nCarbohydrates (g)	10\r\nof which Sugars (g)	4.5\r\nFibre (g)	7.3\r\nProtein (g)	27\r\nSalt (mg)	0.04',3,4,150,'15052023','6464fdbf1d7d0.png'),(12,'Protein Lean Shake Strawberries and Cream','These shakes include protein and a variety of vitamins and minerals to support energy levels. Sufficient dietary protein may fuel muscles by supporting a positive nitrogen balance important for athletic performance goals. B vitamins play an essential role in fat and carbohydrate metabolism*. These gluten-free drinks are available in five flavors, including vanilla bean, strawberries and cream and Swiss chocolate.\r\n\r\nContains 25 g of protein per serving\r\nOnly has 170 calories and 1 g sugar per serving\r\nGNC Total Lean Lean Shake is a quick on-the-go meal replacement solution\r\nEncourages weight loss and BMI management* when combined with regular exercise and a healthy diet\r\nFeatures protein to help support your athletic performance goals\r\nContains B vitamins that aid lipid and carbohydrate metabolism*','INGREDIENTS\r\n\r\nFiltered Water, Milk Protein Concentrate, Milk Protein Isolate and Less than 2%: Acesulfame Potassium, Calcium Caseinate, Carrageenan , Cellulose Gel, Cellulose Gum, DATEM, Lactase, Maltodextrin, Natural and Artificial Flavors, FD&C Blue 1, FD&C Red 3, Salt , Sucralose, Sunflower, Safflower and/or Canola Oil , See label for Vitamin & Mineral Blend , Whey Protein Conc