,3,3,1000,'15052023','646501bf84510.png'),(18,'Diet Protein Complex Cinnamon Cereal Milk','Diet Whey Complex Extreme is a high protein, low calorie shake. It has no added sugar, is low in fat and supercharged with active ingredients. As always with Protein Works, you\'re guaranteed the very best tasting flavours on the planet today.\r\n\r\nIt is the ultimate in weight loss shakes with a market-leading 21.5g of protein in every serving. Diet Whey Complex Extreme is perfect for anyone wanting to add a delicious and nutritious diet protein shake to their routine.','Ingredients\r\n\r\nProtein Blend [Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk) (Emulsifier: Sunflower Lecithin), Soy Protein, Milk Protein Concentrate, Whey Protein Isolate (Milk) (Emulsifier: Sunflower Lecithin)], Konjac Glucomannan, Conjugated Linoleic Acid [Safflower Oil, Glucose Syrup, Sodium Caseinate (Milk), Anti-Caking Agent (Silicon Dioxide), Stabiliser (Tetrasodium Diphosphate), Antioxidant (Vitamin E)], Flavouring, N-Acetyl L-Carnitine, Tri-Calcium Phosphate, Tea Blend (Matcha Green Tea, White Tea Extract, Black Tea Extract), TPW™ Vitamin & Mineral Blend (Tricalcium Phosphate, Vitamin C, Vitamin B5, Vitamin B6, Folic Acid, Vitamin B12), Sweetener (Sucralose).',2,26,150,'15052023','6465028ad7b85.png'),(19,'Iced Coffee Caramel Latte','We’ve taken the classic coffee and transformed it into supercharged fuel for the brain. From high multi-tasking to potent pathway processing. Endless™ Coffee is the most advanced brain food on the market today. It is a delicious caramel latte shake, with only 63 calories, no added sugar and zero crash - you can thank us later.','Skimmed Milk Powder, Coffee Blend [Coffee Powder, Green Coffee Bean Extract], Vitamin & Mineral Blend (Tricalcium Phosphate, Vitamin C, Vitamin B5, Vitamin B6, Folic Acid, Vitamin B12), MCT Powder (Medium Chain Triglycerides (Coconut), Acacia Gum), Flavouring, L-Theanine, Magnesium Oxide, Ashwagandha Extract, Sweetener (Sucralose), Caffeine. WARNING: High Caffeine Content: 100mg/serving. Not suitable for children, pregnant women and persons sensitive to caffeine.\r\n',4,20,1000,'15052023','646511fec74ea.png'),(20,'Micellar Casein Choc Mint Brownie','Ultra fine 100% Micellar Casein is the perfect shake for those who need a slow releasing protein to take before bed.\r\n\r\nCasein protein is a slow releasing protein. Meaning you will have a sustained release of amino acids to the muscles during sleep.\r\n\r\nWith 24 grams of protein, 100% Micellar Casein has a smooth silky texture and can be added to shakes, smoothies, oats and home baking!\r\n','Micellar Casein (Milk), Fat Reduced Cocoa Powder, Flavouring, Sweetener (Sucralose).',2,22,1000,'15052023','6465126ce25d1.png'),(21,'Multi-Protein Banana','Upgrade Multi-Protein gives you the best of both worlds with its innovative blend of premium vegan and dairy proteins combined in one delicious shake. Its unique formulation provides an unparalleled amino acid profile and a multi-phased protein release.\r\n\r\nIt’s our smoothest, creamiest multi-protein shake to date and works well across all our flavours so you won’t be disappointed, whichever you choose.\r\n\r\nUpgrade Multi-Protein is ideal for anyone looking for an exceptional protein shake in terms of ingredients, nutritional content and taste.','Protein Blend [Pea Protein, Whey Protein Concentrate (Milk) (Emulsifier: Sunflower Lecithin), Soy Protein Isolate], Skimmed Milk Powder, Flavourings, Creamer (High Oleic Sunflower Oil, Glucose Syrup, Modified Starch) (Milk), Stabiliser (Guar Gum, Xanthan Gum), Colour (Beetroot Powder), Salt, Sweetener (Sucralose).',2,22,1000,'15052023','646512f1bf91f.png'),(22,'Thermopro Burn','Thermopro Burn is a potent performance formula packed with 15 of the most tried and tested extracts, amino acids, vitamins and minerals.\r\n\r\nSupplied in a convenient capsule format, it is popular as a pre-workout supplement, designed to optimise performance by reducing tiredness and fatigue, supporting 